data.description:
Open House: Sunday, January 14th from 1:00 - 3:00 pm to tour home. 

Fantastic opportunity to move into this cul-de-sac home in the popular Clover Meadows subdivision in Clover, SC. The main floor features hardwood floors, a convenient half bathroom and updated paint. The spacious kitchen features granite counter tops with a pull up bar top opening into the living room. Stainless steel appliances include a stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, and microwave. The living room features a gas burning fireplace and a sliding glass door that leads you onto your patio. The backyard offers wooded privacy. All bedrooms, two full bathrooms and the laundry area with washer / dryer connections are located upstairs. The rooms all have ceiling fans and walk in closets. There is plenty of room for storage with the shed and garage. Located off Hwy 321 and close to shopping, restaurants, retail stores and schools. The clover school system is an award-winning school system. 
Rent is $2,100.00 per month. Available December 2023. No smoking / vaping. Renters insurance is required at all times.

Tenant is responsible for all utilities and landscaping. Owner pays HOA.
